summary: This document is an Indenture dated November 17, 2025, involving Amcor UK Finance PLC as the Issuer, Amcor PLC as the Parent Guarantor, several subsidiaries as Initial Subsidiary Guarantors, and U.S. Bank Trust Company as the Trustee. It outlines the terms for issuing debentures, including definitions, security forms, obligations of the issuer and guarantors, trustee responsibilities, and provisions for satisfaction, discharge, and remedies in case of default. The document also includes covenants, redemption terms, and conditions for defeasance and covenant defeasance.
